{"tid":1746522,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"投票呀！投你老母白票","createTime":"2019-11-22T18:52:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T22:01:06.000Z","uid":316410,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fc8d91f73a3e23130b1b41062e04ab2d863ae77d","tid":1746522,"uid":316410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T18:52:56.000Z","msg":"我身邊都唔少朋友深黃<br />\n最近開曬po屌投票廢<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">投票冇辦法血債票償<br />\n贏咗場選舉都冇7用</span><br />\n叫大家幫手投白票<br />\n<br />\n我屌呀？點解個風吹撚到咁<br />\n選票係公民既權利 更加係責任<br />\n你地唔投係幫緊民建聯助選<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">你有公民意識個陣 <br />\n你上街遊行參與抗爭<br />\n咁點解唔係呢個時候履行翻你既公民責任？</span></strong></span><br />\n選票係我地公民既武器<br />\n依家你同我講要人投白票？？？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n離一離題<br />\n個d日日開ig story屌人個d<br />\n尤其係冇咩上過街參與 <br />\n自己做冷氣軍事or身在外國既人<br />\n你話我兒登仔又好咩都好<br />\n我屌你老母成撚日屌完又唔suggest一個好既做法<br />\n日日屌完為個爽字 以為自己看破紅塵 日日分化<br />\n正睇投白票呢樣都顯出你既智商"},{"pid":"6ae782605d355242f0cad85c08b0ad4699bda8e3","tid":1746522,"uid":316410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T18:57:13.000Z","msg":"推呀屌"},{"pid":"404620493aa0ce7edb492e303611298b680a04b9","tid":1746522,"uid":108571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T18:57:50.000Z","msg":"正皮唔到<br />\n變負皮"},{"pid":"25d2fb4889062c3e631822cbb80c661e899d0b8c","tid":1746522,"uid":103050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T19:01:22.000Z","msg":"屌你，正評變負評<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2655cfae514e3a7c24babe54222f3fce093e5e6","tid":1746522,"uid":199739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T19:02:04.000Z","msg":"【區選撞區36指南】集中投票討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1746415\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1746415</a>"},{"pid":"9c513cbbfbb526e81300aaaba745639c4795db33","tid":1746522,"uid":316410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor